    "\n",
    "The dataset includes transaction records from both the United States and Canada. However, to ensure a consistent and comparable analytical framework, we will filter the dataset to focus exclusively on transactions from the United States.\n",
    "\n",
    "This decision helps reduce potential bias introduced by regional differences such as pricing structures, customer behavior patterns, and market dynamics. By standardizing the dataset to a single geographic region, we ensure that the K-means segmentation reflects a homogeneous customer base, improving the interpretability and reliability of the results."
