    "# 2.2. RFM Feature Construction <a id=\"rfm-feature-construction\"></a>\n",
    "\n",
    "RFM is a widely adopted customer segmentation technique because it summarizes purchasing behavior into three interpretable dimensions that strongly correlate with customer value and engagement."
