    "# relatively small (793 customers), making the additional computational cost negligible while maximizing confidence in the clustering solution.\n",
    "\n",
    "# random_state=42 ( can be any other number):  to ensure reproducibility across runs.\n",
    "# If we run the code again with the same data and parameters in the same environnement, we'll get the same clustering result."
