   "source": [
    "## 4.4. Assigning descriptive segment names for better interpretation\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "As shown above, the labels generated by the K-Means algorithm (cluster_labels) are numerical identifiers (e.g., 0, 1, 2, 3) assigned automatically by the model. While these labels are sufficient for computational processing, they do not provide meaningful information for business interpretation or decision-making.\n",
    "\n",
    "To improve interpretability, these numerical labels are mapped to descriptive segment names based on the behavioral characteristics of each cluster."
   ]
