    "The PCA analysis is conducted in two steps:\n",
    "- Perform PCA and examine the results, including the explained variance ratio, cumulative explained variance, and feature loadings to understand how the principal components represent the original RFM features.\n",
    "- Visualize the K-Means clusters in a two-dimensional scatter plot."
